summary: Secret hide-out dungeon for a group of cultists. They abduct villagers from Riverwood and offer them for summoning rituals.
descriptionHtml:
Delera is a secret hide-out for a group of cultist. At night they sneak arround in the dark and abduct villagers from Riverwood and bring them back to their hide-out. They use these villagers in rituals to make them selves stronger or to summon dark creatures.

This is my first Skyrim mod ever so everything I did in this dungeon was rather new to me. But I did learn a lot about creation kit and there is a good chance I will make more mods in the future.

Dungeon is finished.
In a next patch I will include the quest that comes with the dungeon and improve the Enemies path inside the dungeon.
author: Deets
